summary:
Reputation Stadium Tour: Toronto, Ontario (August 4th, 2018) 

Well good evening, Toronto, and welcome to the Reputation Stadium...
caption:
Reputation Stadium Tour: Toronto, Ontario (August 4th, 2018)

Well good evening, Toronto, and welcome to the Reputation Stadium Tour! You know, here we are… we’re here in Toronto. I’ve been to Toronto before; I know how many things you could be doing on a Saturday night in the summertime, you guys. I’m fully aware of that. Like, you could be doing absolutely anything, and you decided to come hang out with us. Thank you! Here we are… we played here last night, which was absolutely phenomenal. And now we’re playing here tonight, but this is our last show in Toronto. So I don’t know about you guys, but I’m fully, fully preparing myself to use every bit of energy, every bit of heart and soul that I have on this show. Will you so the same, Toronto?
